How to Play
Follow the instructions provided in the game to try to sink all the battleships.
Input your guesses following the format given (e.g., A1, B2).
The game will inform you if your guess is a hit, miss, or if a battleship is sunk.
Keep guessing until you sink all the battleships.
Customization
You can modify the ship names, sizes, and other game settings in the BattleshipGame.java and Battleship.java files.
Feel free to add more features, expand the grid size, or enhance the user interface as you like.
